steps.name: User click on the Continue Button
User click on the Visit Plans
Click on the Visit Plans Table
Click on the Add Visit Configuration
Save the all Single Visit Details
Select the Bathing Assistance Level as a Supervision
Select the Tasks as a Assist With Shower
Click on the Continence And Toileting
save the Continence And Toileting Details
Click on the dressing And Grooming
select the Assistance Level as a Supervision
Click on the Apply Lotion Tasks
Save The Dressing And Grooming Details
Select the Assistance Level as a No Assistance
Select the Assistance Level as  a Limited Assistance
Update the Walk with client Details
User Click on the IADLS Tab
Select the Assistance Level as a Assistance
Select the Make bed Visits Time
User Again click on the IADLs
Select Laundry Assistance Level as a Assistance
Select the Meals Assistance Level No Assistance
User Again click on the IADLS
User select the Medication Assistance Level as Assistance
